Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.17,0:02:09.00,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}正確答案究竟是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.21,0:02:11.92,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}在時間線上遍地盛開的FAKE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.26,0:02:13.30,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}What is reality?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.30,0:02:17.80,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}無論絕望或歡喜  都只是過眼雲煙般的Mirage
