Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.13,0:02:51.21,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}沒錯  Naked Dive!  衝動的Myself
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.38,0:02:54.63,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}只要好奇心不言放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.63,0:02:57.64,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}Making your world!!　 忘我地吶喊吧
